7758a1d1-0d30-4cc6-8aa8-9c39a30f2412	email-drafting	1	## Tone Guidance for HHS Contexts **Communicating to frontline staff:** Direct, clear, supportive. Acknowledge the work. Be honest about challenges. Be specific about what you need. **Communicating to leadership:** Concise, framed around impact and decision needs. Lead with the bottom line. Support with evidence. Make the ask explicit. **Communicating about difficult news:** Lead with the fact, explain the context, clarify what this means for the recipient, offer support or next steps. Don't bury the difficult information. **Communicating policy changes:** What's changing, when, why it matters, what they need to do differently, where to get help if they have questions. 	[0.024343519,0.09809107,0.0026842605,-0.024733527,0.007718996,0.0033683907,0.0062801065,0.027385475,-0.06607904,-0.054286126,-0.034642935,-0.02439667,-0.04600671,-0.04328092,0.03830352,0.016263818,0.02120256,-0.027239688,-0.054510742,-0.017997248,0.019336374,0.025266431,0.013378505,0.10594591,-0.07463208,-0.026871525,-0.0058717653,0.005277693,0.0073985285,-0.010301485,-0.036544517,-0.06889665,0.08639099,0.014047629,-0.0076455195,0.15213826,0.02839754,0.0098480135,-0.0351795,-0.018813558,-0.00089492905,-0.06607617,-0.009904381,0.015904987,-0.0041118194,-0.1038762,0.03247458,0.01965343,-0.028254976,-0.04242967,-0.036827095,-0.086524755,-0.03692006,0.05580096,-0.0339084,0.0136248795,0.026966257,0.04105341,0.02175959,-0.042321775,-0.055949837,-0.04039381,-0.04119197,-0.0044651325,0.009294429,-0.021805247,-0.0007448808,0.004951912,-0.0242535,0.039138313,-0.008966252,-0.05300994,-0.0036814797,-0.03162391,0.010925506,-0.019387336,0.0074252267,0.00472334,0.09877619,-0.025103115,0.032516714,0.014747286,-0.010181502,0.13496463,-0.047944393,-0.0037782863,0.0034659118,-0.0171904,-0.036538277,-0.013024971,0.018244928,-0.037743617,0.022151187,0.003571888,-0.0426924,0.011064549,-0.018431624,-0.045924913,-0.03651777,0.05863873,0.062229753,-0.024279164,0.021795414